{"tid":1682021,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人11月中去鳥取？","createTime":"2019-10-29T20:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T16:03:07.000Z","uid":187938,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a138e204787bc3f9d7dfba446162ead710c4443","tid":1682021,"uid":187938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T20:49:19.000Z","msg":"近呢4個月都好攰，終於book晒機票去日本輕鬆下，但係自己一個人去，好想去食好野，驚一個人難book到餐廳。<br />\n<br />\n個人打算食鳥取和牛同松葉蟹。目標餐廳有 強小亭（和牛燒肉），味處美佐（松葉蟹），たくみ割烹店 （shabu shabu) 。<br />\n<br />\n19-21/11，呢三日我都住係鳥取，有冇巴絲有興趣一齊去食？唔介意幫你比一半錢，真係好想食到。"},{"pid":"64a26820829c6fd4f18019d4bc8edcfe27abfa21","tid":1682021,"uid":187938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T20:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4343c0a652ed785d3ce2eb788bde6f7992a0adca","tid":1682021,"uid":187938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:43:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"600548ef4f6fa845637ac1ed00ff307d279c0273","tid":1682021,"uid":18952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:48:09.000Z","msg":"強小亭我試過 5:30左右入去可以walk in <br />\n個陣我坐HX 落機第一站就係去食燒肉 真心正"},{"pid":"474df6cc4495a3dc86be3fe4645b5806861e404c","tid":1682021,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:48:38.000Z","msg":"好好放鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2ad1d5cef223836d6666d3faca24e91c43fdb8","tid":1682021,"uid":187938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"600548ef4f6fa845637ac1ed00ff307d279c0273","tid":1682021,"uid":18952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:48:09.000Z","msg":"強小亭我試過 5:30左右入去可以walk in <br />\n個陣我坐HX 落機第一站就係去食燒肉 真心正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"我睇過佢地預約時間表，11月好多都就快冇晒位，加上仲要紅葉季節，應該好快full晒"},{"pid":"f0f7d2d922fc3e5150edd83ea81b2f1e64da479d","tid":1682021,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2